screens and the Audi virtual cockpit. The touch screens feature creates a clean and streamlined interior environment while still placing control of the e-Tron&#x2019;s vehicle systems and infotainment literally at the driver&#x2019;s fingertips.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Jaguar i-pace<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Jaguar brings in an award-winning, electric SUV, Jaguar i-pace.&#xA0;The rich, solid finishers surround you and fine twin-needle stitching adds sophistication to the interiors of the car. At night, the crisp white illumination accentuates the exquisite details, winning the hearts of its customers.&#xA0;I-PACE is available with either Sports or Performance seats, both available in a selection of materials and colors.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Mercedes-Benz EQC<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Using renewable raw material for the upholstery, rose gold finishings and widescreen cockpit Mercedes launched the Mercedes Benz EQC. It has unique features such as LED strip light front and rear and the black panel radiator grills. Its interior is both progressive and modern. It has the best sound quality with the exclusive Burmester Surround-Sound System.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Hyundai Kona Electric<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Hyundai Kona Electric is the first all-electric SUV car in India. It can cover up to 452km when fully charged. Hyundai Kona Electric comes in 2 variants &#8211; the base model of Kona Electric is Premium and the top variant is Hyundai Kona Premium Dual Tone. It has three charging methods which include &#x2013; DC fast charging, AC wall box charger, and Portable charger.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Tata Nexon EV<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>The winner of the sub-compact SUV of the year award, Tata Nexon EV, is one of the most impressive EV SUVs. It has a battery capacity of 30.2kWh. It can cover a distance of 312 km when fully charged. Even though it relies on electricity, it generates impressive peak powers of 127bhp. It offers three colors Moonlit Silver, Signature Teal Blue, and Glacier White.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Mahindra e20 Plus<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Empowering the new regenerating brakes, Mahindra e20 Plus is a hatchback electric car, that charges the car whenever brakes are applied. It is a perfect commute vehicle. It can generate maximum torque of 70Nm and power of 25bhp. It has a 3-phase, AC Induction Motor which is equipped with a lithium-ion battery, weighing 84 kg.<\/p>\n<p><strong>MG ZS EV<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>The British MG brand offers a premium EV with zero-emission and no compromise with style. It has a dual-pane panoramic sunroof. It has three driving modes &#x2013; eco, sport, and normal. It has impressive features which include boot space, diamond-cut machined alloy wheels, and power-assisted electric steering. It can cover a distance of about 340km\/charge.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Tata Tigor EV<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>If you want to buy a sedan, Tata Tigor EV is the best choice. It has a 310-liter boot space that facilitates the storage of luggage. It can reach up to 80kmph under normal driving conditions. It covers a distance of about 142 km\/charge. It gives its customers two choices of colors &#8211; Egyptian Blue and Pearlescent White.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Mahindra e-Verito<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>An ideal vehicle for city drives, the e-Verito is a sedan, unlike the e2oPlus. It is powered by a three-phase 72V electric motor that produces 41PS of power and 91Nm of torque. It has a top speed rated at a modest 86 mph. It offers an immense boot space, around 510-litre, which makes it perfect for hauling large bags and equipment. it gives its customers a single choice of Diamond White shade.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Audi e-Tron GT<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Audi e-Tron GT is a luxurious electric car. It is a crossover SUV offering all-wheel drive, high range capabilities, and fast charging. The 5-seater e-Tron GT is available with an Automatic transmission. It gives a maximum torque of 630Nm. The most impressive new element in the e-Tron GT is the Tic Tac-box-size&#xA0;shifter that moves the car from neutral to reverse or drive.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3>Final Words<\/h3>\n<p>After reading all the top 10 electric cars of 2022 in India, did you feel like buying an electric car? And if you are interested in buying electric cars then go and make the right choice by choosing the car that will ease your work.<\/p>\n<p>Make the right choice now by entering into this new era of electric cars.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>In this advanced era of modernization and technology, modern technology has overpowered the world in every walk of life. The drastically increasing world population demands the increase of means of transport. Electric vehicles are&#46;&#46;&#46;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":200024,"featured_media":1562,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[71],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1551"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/200024"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1551"}],"version-history":[{"count":8,"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1551\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1690,"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1551\/revisions\/1690"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1562"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1551"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/vehiclecare.in\/blaze\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1551"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"ht